OL,3,CMan admits arson at mosque but denies
OL,4,Ctrying to hurt anyone
OL,6,FA man has admitted setting fire to a
OL,7,FEast Sussex mosque but denied trying
OL,8,Fto harm anybody.
OL,10,FPeacehaven Mosque was occupied and
OL,11,Flights were on when a fire was
OL,12,Fallegedly started with accelerant on
OL,13,Fits front steps on the night of
OL,14,FOctober 4, 2025.
OL,16,FDuring a hearing at the Old Bailey,
OL,17,FRicky Ryder pleaded guilty to a charge
OL,18,Fof arson that was reckless as to
OL,19,Fwhether life was endangered.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
