OL,3,CMan admits arson at mosque but denies
OL,4,Ctrying to hurt anyone
OL,6,FRyder, 38, of Seaford, pleaded not
OL,7,Fguilty to a charge of arson with
OL,8,Fintent to endanger life and two
OL,9,Ffurther charges of arson relating to
OL,10,Fthe vehicles.
OL,12,FJack Slowey, 34, of Peacehaven,
OL,13,Fpleaded not guilty to all four charges.
OL,15,FA case management hearing is set to
OL,16,Ftake place at the Old Bailey on
OL,17,FOctober 9, ahead of a trial that is
OL,18,Fset for December 1 at Kingston Crown
OL,19,FCourt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
